Package org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson

Class JacksonMonolingualTextValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.JacksonMonolingualTextValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MonolingualTextValue, Value

    public class JacksonMonolingualTextValue
extends Object
implements MonolingualTextValue
    Jackson representation of MonolingualTextValue data used in labels, aliases, and descriptions in JSON. Note that this is distinct from the JSON representation for property values of type MonolingualTextValue, which is implemented in JacksonValueMonolingualText.
    Author:
    Fredo Erxleben
